AmaZulu King Misuzulu kaZwelithini. JOHANNESBURG - King Misuzulu ka Zwelithini says the royal house is saddened by the passing of Princess Thembi Zulu-Ndlovu. The late King Goodwill Zwelithini's sister died at a Newcastle hospital on Friday. She was among the family members who opposed the regency of Misuzulu. READ: Call for unity ahead of King Misuzulu's coronation The King says although they did not always agree, she was still family. Meanwhile, a preliminary date for King Misizulu's coronation has been set for 28 May. President Cyril Ramaphosa has confirmed that he will be attending the ceremony. King Misuzulu kaZwelithini says the royal house is saddened by the passing of Princess Thembi Zulu-Ndlovu. The late King Goodwill Zwelithini's sister died at a Newcastle hospital on Friday. #DStv403 #eNCA pic.twitter.com/4wVBBwYmMk